<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>helios::engine::mechanics::timing::commands</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Timer<sp/>control<sp/>commands<sp/>for<sp/>the<sp/>command<sp/>buffer.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">This<sp/>namespace<sp/>contains<sp/>command<sp/>classes<sp/>used<sp/>to<sp/>request<sp/>timer<sp/>state<sp/>transitions<sp/>through<sp/>the<sp/>command<sp/>system.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>Commands</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>Command<sp/>|<sp/>Description<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|---------|-------------|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>`TimerControlCommand`<sp/>|<sp/>Carries<sp/>a<sp/>`TimerControlContext`<sp/>to<sp/>request<sp/>a<sp/>timer<sp/>state<sp/>transition<sp/>(start,<sp/>pause,<sp/>stop)<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>Usage</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Commands<sp/>are<sp/>typically<sp/>issued<sp/>by<sp/>game-state<sp/>listeners<sp/>or<sp/>systems<sp/>when<sp/>a<sp/>timer<sp/>needs<sp/>to<sp/>change<sp/>state:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```cpp</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">auto<sp/>context<sp/>=<sp/>TimerControlContext{TimerState::Started,<sp/>myTimerId};</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">updateContext.commandBuffer().add&lt;TimerControlCommand&gt;(std::move(context));</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">The<sp/>command<sp/>is<sp/>dispatched<sp/>via<sp/>the<sp/>Visitor<sp/>pattern<sp/>-<sp/>`accept()`<sp/>delegates<sp/>to<sp/>`TimerCommandDispatcher`,<sp/>which<sp/>forwards<sp/>the<sp/>request<sp/>to<sp/>`TimerManager`.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
